{"tid":2286614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★內置 FB、WhatsApp   Nokia 6300 / 8000 4G 發表 售價：49 歐元（約 450 港元）","createTime":"2020-11-15T06:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T23:32:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":103,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"4bae79391008b412456a6ea0ed275bf8c84e28f1","tid":2286614,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:55:04.000Z","msg":"Nokia 6300 4G 和 Nokia 8000 4G 的硬件規格大致相同，例如同樣採用 Qualcomm Snapdragon 210 處理器、512MB RAM、4GB 儲存（支援最高 32GB microSD 擴充）和預載 KaiOS 系統，屏幕同為 QVGA 解像度，分別為 2.4 吋和 2.8 吋，但定價有所分別。配備 30 萬像素相機和聚碳酸酯機殼的 Nokia 6300 4G，售價為 49 歐元（約 450 港元）；配備 200 萬像素相機、玻璃質感聚碳酸酯機殼和仿金屬中框，還有 3D 弧面鍵盤的 Nokia 8000 4G，定價則為 79 歐元（約 725 港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNokia 6300 4G 和 Nokia 8000 4G 兩款手機雖然是功能手機，但亦支援一些智能手機用戶經常用到的程式，例如 WhatsApp、Facebook、YouTube、Google Maps 和 Google Assistant 等，而且內置 4G 無線熱點功能，可以將流動數據與其他裝置分享。Nokia 6300 4G 有黑、白、綠 3 色機身選擇，Nokia 8000 4G 則提供黑、白、藍、金 4 色機身，即日起在歐洲市場發售。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1114-5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F1114-5a.jpg&h=4a34c811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/11/15/nokia-6300-8000-4g-2/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F11%2F15%2Fnokia-6300-8000-4g-2%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BIkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=44c53d8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/11/15/nokia-6300-8000-4g-2/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"a5481f9733beab5f23edbb6606570a530a7e15ed","tid":2286614,"uid":19454,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:55:24.000Z","msg":"no more iphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/